  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "That makes sense, although usually it _should_ be the sum, assuming every index is displayed. I guess when we shouldn't sum it, is if there's indices which aren't shown to the user. Maybe we could have a utility function which sums counts from all indices?",
